column5: New construction with central A/C in garage metal building separate from main house. Comfy 450 sq.ft. room with Queen bed and desk area. Full bath with luxury walk-in shower. Very private with 3 acre property views. Garage Kitchen has no a/c and is a shared space as a parking garage. Fridge, stove, washer/dryer, microwave, toaster oven, pots, pans and utensils included. Bottled water and all toiletries provided.
